## Rules

### CICD-001: Build Time Gate
severity: ERROR
scope: all CI pipeline configurations
rule: The full CI build and test suite MUST complete within the configured time limit. Pipelines exceeding this threshold MUST be optimized or parallelized.
threshold: max_build_minutes=10, min_test_coverage_gate=80
example_correct: |
  # Parallelized test jobs — total time 7 minutes
  jobs:
    test-unit: ...
    test-integration: ...
example_incorrect: |
  # Sequential jobs taking 25 minutes

### CICD-002: Automated Quality Gates
severity: ERROR
scope: all pull request pipelines
rule: Every pull request MUST pass automated lint, type-check, and test stages before merging. Manual bypasses of quality gates are prohibited. Deployments MUST only proceed from a green pipeline.
threshold: min_test_coverage_gate=80
example_correct: |
  # .github/workflows/ci.yml enforces ruff, mypy, pytest
example_incorrect: |
  # Merging with --no-verify skipping pre-commit hooks
